<eesti>1. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 1 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lds&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>General Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse &uuml;lesanne </eesti>
<inglise>Purpose of the Act </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;esolev seadus reguleerib suhteid kalap&uuml;&uuml;gil ja veetaimede kogumisel. </eesti>
<inglise>This Act regulates relations concerning fishing and the collection of aquatic plants. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse kohaldamine </eesti>
<inglise>Application of Act </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolev seadus kehtib Eesti Vabariigi majandusv&ouml;&ouml;ndis majandusv&ouml;&ouml;ndi seadusest (RT 1993, 7, 105) tulenevate erisustega. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) This Act applies in the exclusive economic zone of the Republic of Estonia with the exceptions arising from the Exclusive Economic Zone Act (RT 1993, 7, 105). </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) K&auml;esolev seadus ei reguleeri suhteid kalade kasvatamisel ja p&uuml;&uuml;gil kalakasvatuslikes rajatistes nagu tiigid, sumbad, basseinid. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) This Act does not regulate relations concerning the breeding and catching of fish in fish breeding structures, such as ponds, wells and pools. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) K&auml;esolev seadus reguleerib kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki Eesti lipudokumenti omava laevaga v&auml;ljaspool Eesti Vabariigi jurisdiktsiooni oleval veealal niiv&otilde;rd, kuiv&otilde;rd p&uuml;&uuml;gikoha asukohariigi &otilde;igusakt v&otilde;i p&uuml;&uuml;gikoha kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki reguleeriv rahvusvaheline leping ei s&auml;testa teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) This Act regulates fishing by vessels for which Estonian papers of nationality have been issued in waters beyond the jurisdiction of the Republic of Estonia in so far as the legislation of the state where fishing is carried out or an international agreement regulating fishing in the fishing area do not provide otherwise. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>Kalap&uuml;&uuml;k ja veetaimede kogumine </eesti>
<inglise>Fishing and collection of aquatic plants </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kalap&uuml;&uuml;k on k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses tegevus, mille eesm&auml;rgiks on kala ja j&otilde;esilmu, j&otilde;ev&auml;hi ning teiste veeselgrootute (edaspidi kala) h&otilde;ivamine nende kinnip&uuml;&uuml;dmise v&otilde;i surmamise teel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) For the purposes of this Act, fishing is an activity the aim of which is the capture of fish, river lamprey, crayfish and other aquatic invertebrates (hereinafter fish) by catching or killing them. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Veetaimede kogumine on k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses agariku (Furcellaria lumbricalis) p&uuml;&uuml;k merest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purpose of this Act, the collection of aquatic plants is the gathering of agar-agar (Furcellaria lumbricalis) from the sea. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) P&uuml;&uuml;gikorda seatud p&uuml;&uuml;givahenditega viibimine veekogul v&otilde;i selle kaldal v&otilde;rdsustatakse kalap&uuml;&uuml;giga. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Staying on a body of water or on the shore thereof with fishing gear prepared for fishing is deemed to be equal to fishing. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>Kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi ja veetaimede kogumise p&otilde;hin&otilde;ue </eesti>
<inglise>Basic requirement regarding fishing and collection of aquatic plants </inglise>
<eesti>Kalap&uuml;&uuml;gil ja veetaimede kogumisel tuleb s&auml;ilitada nende varude taastumisv&otilde;ime ja veekogude tootlikkus ning v&auml;ltida ebasoovitavaid muutusi veekogude &ouml;kos&uuml;steemis. </eesti>
<inglise>During fishing and the collection of aquatic plants, the reproduction capacity of their stocks and the productivity of bodies of water shall be preserved and undesirable changes to the ecosystem of bodies of water shall be avoided. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Omandi&otilde;igus </eesti>
<inglise>Right of ownership </inglise>
<eesti>(1) P&uuml;&uuml;dja omandi&otilde;igus kalale tekib h&otilde;ivamisega, kui see ei ole vastuolus k&auml;esoleva seadusega ja ei rikuta teiste isikute &otilde;igusi. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The right of ownership of a fish is created for the person who captures the fish unless this is in conflict with this Act or violates the rights of other persons. </inglise>
<eesti>Kala on peremehetu, kui ta on looduslikus vabaduses. </eesti>
<inglise>A fish is ownerless if it is free in nature. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Agarik meres on riigi omandis. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Agar-agar in the sea is in the ownership of the state. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaldale uhutud agarik on kaldal asuva kinnisasja omaniku omandis. </eesti>
<inglise>Agar-agar washed ashore is in the ownership of the owner of the immovable property located on the shore. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Omandi&otilde;igus veekogule on kehtestatud veeseadusega (RT I 1994, 40, 655; 1996, 13, 240; 1998, 2, 47; 61, 987; 1999, 10, 155; 54, 583; 95, 843). </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The right of ownership of a body of water is provided by the Water Act (RT I 1994, 40, 655; 1996, 13, 240; 1998, 2, 47; 61, 987; 1999, 10, 155; 54, 583; 95, 843). </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igus </eesti>
<inglise>Fishing rights </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kala p&uuml;&uuml;takse kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Fishing shall be performed pursuant to fishing rights. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) S&otilde;ltuvalt kasutatavatest p&uuml;&uuml;givahenditest eristatakse &otilde;ngep&uuml;&uuml;gi-, v&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;gi-, harrastusp&uuml;&uuml;gi-, piiratud p&uuml;&uuml;gi- ja kutselist p&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igust. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Depending on the fishing gear used, a difference is made in terms of fishing rights between line fishing, the catching of crayfish, recreational fishing, restricted fishing and commercial fishing. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Iga&uuml;ks tohib kasutada k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igusi, kui ta on sooritanud nende tekkimiseks vajalikud toimingud. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Everyone may exercise the fishing rights specified in subsection (2) of this section if he or she has performed the acts necessary to create such rights. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igus on tasuta v&otilde;i tasuline. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Fishing rights are either free of charge or subject to a fee. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. (Kehtetu - 12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. (Repealed - 12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>2. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 2 </inglise>
<eesti>Kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi korraldamine </eesti>
<inglise>Organisation of Fishing </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. (Kehtetu - 08.12.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 95, 843) </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. (Repealed - 08.12.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 95, 843) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. (Kehtetu - 08.12.1999 j&otilde;ust.01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 95, 843) </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. (Repealed - 08.12.1999 entered into force 01.01.2000 - RT I 1999, 95, 843) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>&Otilde;ngep&uuml;&uuml;k </eesti>
<inglise>Line fishing </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Iga&uuml;ks tohib tasuta ja p&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igust vormistamata &uuml;he lihtk&auml;si&otilde;ngega kala p&uuml;&uuml;da riigile ja kohalikule omavalitsusele kuuluval v&otilde;i eraomanikule kuuluval avalikuks kasutamiseks m&auml;&auml;ratud veekogul, arvestades lubatud p&uuml;&uuml;giaegade, -kohtade ja kalaliikide kohta kehtestatud piiranguid. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Everyone may fish, free of charge and without having applied for the right to fish, with one simple hand line on a body of water belonging to the state or a local government or on a privately owned body of water which is designated for public use, taking into consideration restrictions concerning the permitted fishing seasons, fishing areas and species of fish. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kinnisasja omaniku loal tohib &uuml;he lihtk&auml;si&otilde;ngega kala p&uuml;&uuml;da: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) With the permission of the owner of the immovable, fishing with one simple hand line is permitted: </inglise>
<eesti>1) eraomanikule kuuluval avalikuks kasutamiseks m&auml;&auml;ramata veekogul; </eesti>
<inglise>1) on a privately owned body of water which is not designated for public use; </inglise>
<eesti>2) siseveekogu poolt &uuml;leujutatud kinnisasjal v&otilde;i selle osal; </eesti>
<inglise>2) on an immovable or part thereof which is flooded by an internal water body; </inglise>
<eesti>3) eraomanikule kuuluval avalikuks kasutamiseks m&auml;&auml;ratud veekogul p&auml;ikeseloojangust p&auml;ikeset&otilde;usuni. </eesti>
<inglise>3) from sunset to sunrise on a privately owned body of water which is designated for public use. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Otilde;ngep&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igus on iga&uuml;he eluaegne &otilde;igus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Every person has the lifelong right to fish by line. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>Harrastusp&uuml;&uuml;k </eesti>
<inglise>Recreational fishing </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Iga&uuml;ks tohib kalastuskaardi alusel harrastusp&uuml;&uuml;givahenditega kala p&uuml;&uuml;da riigile ja kohalikule omavalitsusele kuuluval veekogul v&otilde;i eraomanikule kuuluval avalikuks kasutamiseks m&auml;&auml;ratud veekogul, arvestades lubatud p&uuml;&uuml;giaegade, -kohtade ja kalaliikide kohta kehtestatud piiranguid. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) On the basis of a fishing card, everyone may fish using fishing tackle on a body of water belonging to the state or a local government or on a privately owned body of water which is designated for public use, taking into consideration restrictions concerning the permitted fishing seasons, fishing areas and species of fish. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kinnisasja omaniku loal tohib harrastusp&uuml;&uuml;givahenditega kala p&uuml;&uuml;da: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) With the permission of the owner of the immovable, fishing is permitted with fishing tackle: </inglise>
<eesti>1) eraomanikule kuuluval avalikuks kasutamiseks m&auml;&auml;ramata veekogul; </eesti>
<inglise>1) on a privately owned body of water which is not designated for public use; </inglise>
<eesti>2) siseveekogu poolt &uuml;leujutatud kinnisasjal v&otilde;i selle osal; </eesti>
<inglise>2) on an immovable or part thereof which is flooded by an internal water body; </inglise>
<eesti>3) eraomanikule kuuluval avalikuks kasutamiseks m&auml;&auml;ratud veekogul p&auml;ikeseloojangust p&auml;ikeset&otilde;usuni. </eesti>
<inglise>3) from sunset to sunrise on a privately owned body of water which is designated for public use. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Harrastusp&uuml;&uuml;givahendid on: </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The following items are fishing tackle: </inglise>
<eesti>1) spinning, vedel, sikut, lend&otilde;ng, p&otilde;hja&otilde;ng, krunda, ankurdamata und, k&auml;si&otilde;ng v&otilde;i enam kui &uuml;ks lihtk&auml;si&otilde;ng; </eesti>
<inglise>1) spinning reels, trolling lines, pulling devices, fly hooks, bottom lines, krunda, unanchored trimmers, hand lines or more than one simple hand line; </inglise>
<eesti>2) harpuunip&uuml;ss ja harpuun; </eesti>
<inglise>2) harpoon guns and harpoons; </inglise>
<eesti>3) haake&otilde;ng. </eesti>
<inglise>3) hooks. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Haake&otilde;nge tohib kasutada merel, Peipsi, L&auml;mmi- ja Pihkva j&auml;rvel. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Hooks may be used at sea and on Lake Peipus, Lake L&auml;mmij&auml;rv and Lake Pskov. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Harrastusp&uuml;&uuml;gi &otilde;igus tekib kalastuskaardi ostmise p&auml;evast, mis m&auml;rgitakse kalastuskaardile. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The right to fish for recreation commences on the day of purchase of a fishing card, which shall be entered on the fishing card. </inglise>
<eesti>Kalastuskaardi kehtivusaeg ei tohi &uuml;letada &uuml;hte kalendriaastat. </eesti>
<inglise>The term of validity of a fishing card shall not exceed one calendar year. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kalastuskaardile lisatakse teave lubatud p&uuml;&uuml;givahendite, olulisemate p&uuml;&uuml;gikitsenduste ja nende piirkondade kohta, kus kalastuskaart ei kehti. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) Information concerning permitted fishing gear, essential fishing restrictions and areas for which the fishing card is not valid shall be appended to a fishing card. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Keskkonnaministril on &otilde;igus m&auml;&auml;rata piirkonnad, kus kalavarude kaitse eesm&auml;rgil rakendatakse piiranguid kala p&uuml;&uuml;da soovivate isikute arvu, p&uuml;&uuml;givahendite v&otilde;i p&uuml;&uuml;tavate kalade suhtes. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) The Minister of the Environment has the right to designate areas where limitations apply on the number of persons who wish to fish, on fishing gear or on fish caught with the aim of conserving fishery resources. </inglise>
<eesti>Nendes piirkondades kehtib kalastuskaart koos lisalehega. </eesti>
<inglise>In such areas, a fishing card is valid only with a supplement sheet. </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Kalastuskaardi annab Keskkonnaministeeriumi maakondlik keskkonnateenistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) Fishing cards shall be issued by the county environmental services of the Ministry of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>Keskkonnaminister v&otilde;ib halduslepinguga anda kalastuskaardi andmise &otilde;iguse kohalikule omavalitsusele v&otilde;i harrastuskalastajate registreeritud &uuml;hendusele. </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of the Environment may, on the basis of a contract under public law, delegate the right to issue fishing cards to local governments or to a registered association of recreational fishermen. </inglise>
<eesti>(9) Kalastuskaart kehtib kogu Eesti territooriumil. </eesti>
<inglise>(9) Fishing cards are valid throughout the territory of Estonia. </inglise>
<eesti>Kalastuskaardi vormi kehtestab keskkonnaminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The format of fishing cards shall be established by the Minister of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;k </eesti>
<inglise>Catching of crayfish </inglise>
<eesti>(1) V&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;gi suhtes kohaldatakse piiratud p&uuml;&uuml;gi kohta s&auml;testatut, kui k&auml;esolevast paragrahvist ei tulene teisiti. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The provisions concerning restricted fishing apply to the catching of crayfish, unless otherwise provided for in this section. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;giloa saamise taotluse esitamist taotletava aasta 1. jaanuariks ei n&otilde;uta. </eesti>
<inglise>It is not a requirement that an application for a permit for the catching of crayfish be submitted by 1 January of the year for which the licence is applied for. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) V&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse annab v&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;giluba. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The right to catch crayfish is granted by a permit for the catching of crayfish. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) V&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;giloa annab p&uuml;&uuml;giasukoha keskkonnateenistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Permits for the catching of crayfish shall be issued by the environmental service of the corresponding catching area. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Lubatud v&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;givahendid on v&auml;hinatt ja v&auml;him&otilde;rd. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The only permitted equipment for catching crayfish are dip-nets and traps. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) V&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;giloaga m&auml;&auml;ratakse lubatud p&uuml;&uuml;givahendid, nende arv ja p&uuml;&uuml;da lubatud v&auml;hkide arv. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) A permit for the catching of crayfish shall set out the permitted catching equipment, the amount thereof and the number of crayfish it is permitted to catch. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) V&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;giloa ja p&uuml;&uuml;giandmete esitamise vormi ning p&uuml;&uuml;giandmete esitamise t&auml;htaja kehtestab keskkonnaminister. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The format of permits for the catching of crayfish, the format for the submission of catch data and the term for submission of catch data shall be established by the Minister of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13. </inglise>
<eesti>Kutseline p&uuml;&uuml;k </eesti>
<inglise>Commercial fishing </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahenditega tohib kala p&uuml;&uuml;da ettev&otilde;tjana &auml;riregistris registreeritud isik kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa alusel siseveekogudel, piiriveekogudel, merel, Eesti Vabariigi majandusv&ouml;&ouml;ndis v&otilde;i v&auml;ljaspool Eesti Vabariigi jurisdiktsiooni oleval veealal. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A person who is registered in the commercial register as an undertaking may fish with commercial fishing gear on the basis of a fishing permit on internal water bodies, on transboundary water bodies, at sea, in the exclusive economic zone of the Republic of Estonia, or outside the waters under the jurisdiction of the Republic of Estonia. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahendid on &otilde;ngejadad, nakkep&uuml;&uuml;nised, l&otilde;ksp&uuml;&uuml;nised, kurnp&uuml;&uuml;nised ja traalp&uuml;&uuml;nised. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Commercial fishing gear means longlines, gillnets and entangling nets, traps, seine nets and trawls. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Otilde;iguse kutseliseks kalap&uuml;&uuml;giks annab kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba, mis v&otilde;ib olla kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba v&otilde;i kaluri kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The right to fish commercially is granted by a fishing permit, which may be either the fishing permit of a fishing vessel or a fisherman's fishing permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kalalaev on kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahenditega varustatud laev. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A fishing vessel is a vessel equipped with commercial fishing gear. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Vabariigi Valitsus asutab kalalaevade riikliku registri. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) The Government of the Republic shall establish a state register of fishing vessels. </inglise>
<eesti>Registrisse kantakse v&auml;hemalt seitsme meetri pikkused kalalaevad, nende tehnilised parameetrid ja kalap&uuml;&uuml;giga seonduvad andmed. </eesti>
<inglise>All fishing vessels with an overall length of at least seven metres shall be entered in the register together with their technical specifications and data related to fishing. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13 (1). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13 (1). </inglise>
<eesti>Kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba </eesti>
<inglise>Fishing permit of fishing vessel </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba annab &otilde;iguse kalap&uuml;&uuml;giks kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahenditega merel kuni Eesti Vabariigi majandusv&ouml;&ouml;ndi v&auml;lispiirini, v&auml;ljaspool Eesti Vabariigi jurisdiktsiooni oleval veealal, kui kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse seal tagab riik, v&otilde;i avamerel. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The fishing permit of a fishing vessel grants the right to fish with commercial fishing gear at sea up to the external border of the exclusive economic zone of the Republic of Estonia, outside the waters under the jurisdiction of the Republic of Estonia if the state guarantees the right to fish there, or on the open sea. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba antakse &auml;riregistris registreeritud ettev&otilde;tjale tema seaduslikus valduses oleva Eesti merelaeva-, siseveelaeva- v&otilde;i v&auml;ikelaeva- tunnistusega kalalaevale, millel on kalalaevatunnistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) A fishing permit of a fishing vessel shall be issued to an undertaking registered in the commercial register regarding a fishing vessel in the legal possession thereof for which an Estonian certificate of a sea-going vessel or inland vessel or small craft and a fishing vessel certificate have been issued. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa annab Keskkonnaministeerium. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Fishing permits of fishing vessels shall be issued by the Ministry of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;ib asendada temale antud kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloas nimetatud kalalaeva teise tema &otilde;igusp&auml;rases valduses oleva Eesti merelaevatunnistust ja kalalaevatunnistust omava kalalaevaga, teavitades sellest kirjalikult kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa andjat. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) An undertaking may replace the fishing vessel specified in a fishing permit of a fishing vessel issued to the undertaking with another fishing vessel in the legal possession thereof for which an Estonian certificate of a sea-going vessel and a fishing vessel certificate have been issued, in which case the undertaking shall inform the issuer of the fishing permit thereof in writing. </inglise>
<eesti>Kalalaeva asendamise j&otilde;ustumiseks v&auml;ljastab kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa andja ettev&otilde;tjale teate saamisest kahe n&auml;dala jooksul uue kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa. </eesti>
<inglise>In order that the replacement of the fishing vessel may take effect, the issuer of the fishing permit shall issue a new fishing permit to the undertaking within two weeks as of receipt of the notice. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13 (2). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13 (2). </inglise>
<eesti>Kaluri kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba </eesti>
<inglise>Fisherman's fishing permit </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kaluri kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba annab &otilde;iguse kalap&uuml;&uuml;giks, v&auml;lja arvatud lestap&uuml;&uuml;k, kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahenditega merel kuni 20 m samas&uuml;gavusjooneni, Peipsi, L&auml;mmi- ja Pihkva j&auml;rvel, Narva j&otilde;el ja Narva veehoidlal v&otilde;i siseveekogul. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A fisherman's fishing permit grants the right to fish, except fishing for flounder, with commercial fishing gear at sea up to the 20 m isobath, on Lake Peipus, Lake L&auml;mmij&auml;rv and Lake Pskov, on Narva River and the Narva reservoir, or on an internal water body. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaluri kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba lestap&uuml;&uuml;giks annab &otilde;iguse lesta p&uuml;&uuml;da merel, s&otilde;ltumata mere s&uuml;gavusest. </eesti>
<inglise>A fisherman's fishing permit for the fishing of flounder grants the right to fish flounder at sea, irrespective of the depth of the sea. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kalur k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on f&uuml;&uuml;siline isik, kes vahetult p&uuml;&uuml;ab kala kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahenditega. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) For the purposes of this Act, a fisherman is a natural person who catches fish himself or herself with commercial fishing gear. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaluri poolt kalap&uuml;&uuml;gile kaasav&otilde;etavate isikute arv ei ole piiratud. </eesti>
<inglise>The number of persons accompanying a fisherman who is fishing is not limited. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Kaluri kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba antakse &auml;riregistris registreeritud ettev&otilde;tjale. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A fisherman's fishing permit shall be issued to an undertaking registered in the commercial register. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui ettev&otilde;tja ei ole ise kalur, n&auml;idatakse kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloas ettev&otilde;tja kirjaliku taotluse alusel kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki vahetult teostava kaluri nimi. </eesti>
<inglise>If the undertaking itself is not a fisherman, the name of the fisherman who catches fish on the basis of a written application from the undertaking shall be indicated in the fishing permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Ettev&otilde;tja v&otilde;ib asendada temale antud kaluri kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloas nimetatud kaluri, teavitades sellest kirjalikult kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa andjat. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) An undertaking may replace the fisherman specified in a fisherman's fishing permit issued to the undertaking, in which case the undertaking shall inform the issuer of the fishing permit thereof in writing. </inglise>
<eesti>Kaluri asendamise j&otilde;ustumiseks v&auml;ljastab kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa andja ettev&otilde;tjale teate saamisest viie t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul uue kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa. </eesti>
<inglise>In order that the replacement of the fisherman might take effect, the issuer of the fishing permit shall issue a new fishing permit to the undertaking within five working days as of receipt of the notice. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kaluri kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa annab vastava maakonna keskkonnateenistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Fisherman's fishing permits shall be issued by the corresponding county environmental services. </inglise>
<eesti>Kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa andja merel ja mitme maakonna piiresse j&auml;&auml;val siseveekogul m&auml;&auml;rab keskkonnaminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The issuer of fisherman's fishing permits for fishing at sea and on internal water bodies located within the boundaries of several counties shall be designated by the Minister of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13 (3). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13 (3). </inglise>
<eesti>Piiratud p&uuml;&uuml;k </eesti>
<inglise>Restricted fishing </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi luba annab &otilde;iguse kalap&uuml;&uuml;giks piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahenditega: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A restricted fishing permit grants the following persons the right to fish with restricted fishing gear in the following places: </inglise>
<eesti>1) mereranna piiresse ulatuva kinnistu f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust omanikule ja merega piirneva kohaliku omavalitsuse poolt piiritletud ala alalisele elanikule kinnistu asukoha v&otilde;i alalise elaniku elukoha maakonnaga piirneval mereakvatooriumi osal kuni 20 meetri samas&uuml;gavusjooneni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) a natural person who is the owner of a registered immovable extending to the sea coast and a permanent resident of an area bordering on the sea and delimited by a local government is granted the right to fish up to the 20 m isobath in marine waters bordering on the county in which the registered immovable is located or the permanent resident resides; </inglise>
<eesti>2) Peipsi, L&auml;mmi- ja Pihkva j&auml;rve ranna piiresse ulatuva kinnistu f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust omanikule ja kohaliku omavalitsuse poolt piiritletud ala alalisele elanikule kinnistu asukoha v&otilde;i alalise elaniku elukoha maakonnaga piirneval j&auml;rveakvatooriumi osal kuni &uuml;he kilomeetri laiusel veealal; </eesti>
<inglise>2) a natural person who is the owner of a registered immovable extending to the shore of Lake Peipus, Lake L&auml;mmij&auml;rv or Lake Pskov and a permanent resident of an area delimited by a local government is granted the right to fish up to one kilometre from the shore of the lake in waters bordering on the county in which the registered immovable is located or the permanent resident resides; </inglise>
<eesti>3) V&otilde;rtsj&auml;rve ranna, j&auml;rve v&otilde;i paisj&auml;rve kalda piiresse ulatuva kinnistu f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust omanikule j&auml;rvel v&otilde;i paisj&auml;rvel, mille ranna v&otilde;i kalda piiresse kinnistu ulatub; </eesti>
<inglise>3) a natural person who is the owner of a registered immovable extending to the shore of Lake V&otilde;rtsj&auml;rv or another lake or reservoir is granted the right to fish on the lake or reservoir to the shore of which the registered immovable extends; </inglise>
<eesti>4) vooluveekogu kalda piiresse ulatuva kinnistu f&uuml;&uuml;silisest isikust omanikule kinnistuga piirnevale v&otilde;i kinnistu piiresse j&auml;&auml;val vooluveekogu osal. </eesti>
<inglise>4) a natural person who is the owner of a registered immovable extending to the bank of a flowing body of water is granted the right to fish on the part of the body of water which borders on or is within the immovable. </inglise>
<eesti>(08.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </eesti>
<inglise>(08.02.2001 entered into force 26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </inglise>
<eesti>(1 (1)) Kui saarel asuv kohalik omavalitsus&uuml;ksus ei piirne merega, on keskkonnaministril &otilde;igus laiendada piiratud p&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igust sellise kohaliku omavalitsuse taotluses n&auml;idatud territooriumil elavatele alalistele elanikele ja m&auml;&auml;rata p&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse realiseerimiseks mereakvatooriumi osa. </eesti>
<inglise>(1 (1)) If a local government located on an island does not border on the sea, the Minister of the Environment has the right to extend restricted fishing rights to the permanent residents of the local government territory indicated in the application and to designate a part of the marine waters where the fishing rights may be exercised. </inglise>
<eesti>(08.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </eesti>
<inglise>(08.02.2001 entered into force 26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahendid merel, Peipsi, L&auml;mmi- ja Pihkva j&auml;rvel ning V&otilde;rtsj&auml;rvel on kuni kolm nakkev&otilde;rku, &uuml;ks kuni &uuml;hemeetrise suuk&otilde;rgusega &auml;&auml;rem&otilde;rd v&otilde;i kuni 250st konksust koosnev p&otilde;hja&otilde;ngejada. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Restricted fishing gear at sea and on Lakes Peipus, L&auml;mmij&auml;rv, Pskov and V&otilde;rtsj&auml;rv means up to three entangling nets, one fyke net with a height of up to one meter, or a bottom longline consisting of up to 250 hooks. </inglise>
<eesti>Teistel siseveekogudel on piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi vahendid nakkev&otilde;rk, kaldanoot, kuurits, liiv, kuni &uuml;hemeetrise suuk&otilde;rgusega m&otilde;rd ja kuni 100st konksust koosnev p&otilde;hja&otilde;ngejada. </eesti>
<inglise>Restricted fishing gear on other internal water bodies means an entangling net, a beach seine, a dragnet, a hoopnet, a fyke net with a height of up to one meter and a bottom longline consisting of up to 100 hooks. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa annab keskkonnaministri volitatud keskkonnateenistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Restricted fishing permits shall be issued by the environmental service authorised by the Minister of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa vormi, taotlemisel esitatavate dokumentide loetelu ja lubade v&auml;ljaandmise korra kehtestab keskkonnaminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The format of restricted fishing permits, the list of documents to be submitted upon application and the procedure for the issue of permits shall be established by the Minister of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loaga m&auml;&auml;ratakse lubatud p&uuml;&uuml;givahendid, v&auml;ljap&uuml;&uuml;gimahud, p&uuml;&uuml;giajad ja kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi koht. </eesti>
<inglise>A restricted fishing permit shall set out the permitted fishing gear, the quota allocations, and the fishing seasons and areas. </inglise>
<eesti>Kohaliku omavalitsuse taotluse alusel v&otilde;ib keskkonnaminister piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa andmise &otilde;iguse halduslepinguga &uuml;le anda kohalikule omavalitsusele. </eesti>
<inglise>On the basis of an application from a local government, the Minister of the Environment may transfer the right to issue restricted fishing permits to a local government by a contract under public law. </inglise>
<eesti>(08.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </eesti>
<inglise>(08.02.2001 entered into force 26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Eraomanikule kuuluvale veekogule tohib piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi luba anda veekogu omanikule v&otilde;i tema kirjaliku n&otilde;usoleku olemasolul kolmandale isikule. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) A restricted fishing permit for fishing on privately owned bodies of water may be issued to the owner of the body of water or, with the written consent of the owner, to a third person. </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igus tekib piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loaga m&auml;&auml;ratud kuup&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Restricted fishing rights commence on the date designated in the permit. </inglise>
<eesti>Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa kehtivusaeg ei tohi &uuml;letada &uuml;hte kalendriaastat. </eesti>
<inglise>The term of validity of a restricted fishing permit shall not exceed one calendar year. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Keskkonnaminister kehtestab, l&auml;htudes kalavaru seisundist ja siseveekogu pindalast, lubatud aastase p&uuml;&uuml;givahendite arvu ja vajadusel ka v&auml;ljap&uuml;&uuml;gimahu maakondade ja omavalitsuste l&otilde;ikes ning merel kuni 20 m samas&uuml;gavusjooneni. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The Minister of the Environment shall establish, depending on the state of fishery resources and the area of an internal water body, the annual permitted amount of fishing gear and, if necessary, the quota allocation per county and local government and at sea up to the 20 m isobath. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Isikule, kes ei ole ranna v&otilde;i kalda piires oleva kinnistu v&otilde;i selle osa, hoonestus&otilde;iguse v&otilde;i korteriomandi omanik, v&otilde;ib piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa anda vaid juhul, kui lubatud aastane p&uuml;&uuml;givahendite arv v&otilde;i lubatud v&auml;ljap&uuml;&uuml;gimaht on suurem kui k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud isikute taotlustes v&otilde;i taotlused puuduvad. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) A restricted fishing permit may be issued to a person who is not the owner of a registered immovable or a part thereof located on the shore or bank of a water body or who does not hold a right of superficies or apartment ownership concerning such a registered immovable only if the annual permitted amount of fishing gear or the permitted quota allocation is higher than that indicated in the applications from persons specified in subsection (1) of this section or if there are no such applications. </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Kui lubatud aastane p&uuml;&uuml;givahendite arv v&otilde;i lubatud v&auml;ljap&uuml;&uuml;gimaht ei v&otilde;imaldada rahuldada k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud isikute taotlusi ja taotlejad ei ole p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imaluste jaotamises omavahel kokku leppinud, jaotatakse lubatud p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imalused k&otilde;ikide taotlejate vahel v&otilde;rdselt, l&uuml;hendades vajadusel ka p&uuml;&uuml;giloa kehtivuse aega. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) If the annual permitted amount of fishing gear or the permitted quota allocation does not enable applications from persons specified in subsection (1) of this section to be satisfied and if the applicants do not come to a mutual agreement concerning the division of fishing possibilities, the permitted fishing possibilities shall be divided equally between all applicants and, if necessary, the term of validity of the fishing permit shall be reduced. </inglise>
<eesti>(9) Taotlus piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa saamiseks tuleb esitada hiljemalt taotletava aasta 1. jaanuariks. </eesti>
<inglise>(9) Applications for a restricted fishing permit shall be submitted not later than by 1 January of the year for which the permit is applied for. </inglise>
<eesti>Hiljem esitatud taotlus rahuldatakse ainult p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imaluste olemasolul. </eesti>
<inglise>Applications submitted later shall be satisfied only if fishing possibilities remain. </inglise>
<eesti>(10) Piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa andmisest keeldutakse, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(10) A restricted fishing permit shall be refused if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) loa taotlejal on rohkem kui &uuml;ks kehtiv karistus kalap&uuml;&uuml;gin&otilde;uete rikkumise eest; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the applicant has more than one punishment in force for violation of fishing requirements; </inglise>
<eesti>2) taotlus ei vasta n&otilde;uetele v&otilde;i on loa taotleja esitanud taotluses valeandmeid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the application does not conform to the requirements or the applicant for the permit submits false information in the application; </inglise>
<eesti>3) loa taotleja on esitanud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi kohta valeandmeid v&otilde;i on j&auml;tnud andmed t&auml;htajaliselt esitamata; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the applicant submits false information on fishing or fails to submit the information within the set term; </inglise>
<eesti>4) loa taotleja on j&auml;tnud t&auml;htaegselt maksmata kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse tasu. </eesti>
<inglise>4) the applicant fails to pay the fee for the right to fish within the set term. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13 (4). </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13 (4). </inglise>
<eesti>Kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa andmine </eesti>
<inglise>Issue of commercial fishing permit </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi luba antakse lubatud aastase v&auml;ljap&uuml;&uuml;gimahu, p&uuml;&uuml;gip&auml;evade arvu, p&uuml;&uuml;givahendite arvu v&otilde;i kalalaevade arvu (edaspidi p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imalused) piires t&auml;htajaliselt ja mitte kauemaks kui &uuml;heks kalendriaastaks. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) A commercial fishing permit shall be issued within the limits of the permitted annual quota allocation, number of fishing days, amount of fishing gear or number of fishing vessels (hereinafter fishing possibilities) for a specified term but for not longer than one calendar year. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa taotlus esitatakse hiljemalt taotletavale aastale eelneva aasta 1. detsembriks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) An application for a commercial fishing permit shall be submitted not later than by 1 December of the year preceding the year for which the permit is applied for. </inglise>
<eesti>Keskkonnaminister v&otilde;ib m&otilde;juvatel p&otilde;hjustel taotluste esitamise t&auml;htaega pikendada. </eesti>
<inglise>The Minister of the Environment may, with good reason, extend the term for submission of applications. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Taotletava aasta p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imalused kehtestab keskkonnaminister taotletavale aastale eelneva aasta 1. novembriks, kui p&uuml;&uuml;gikoha asukohariik v&otilde;i p&uuml;&uuml;gikoha kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki reguleeriv rahvusvaheline organisatsioon ei anna p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imalusi hilisemal ajal. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The fishing possibilities for the year for which the permit is applied for shall be established by the Minister of the Environment by 1 November of the preceding year, unless the state where the fishing area is located or the international organisation regulating fishing in the fishing area establishes the fishing possibilities at a later time. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi lubade taotlemisel esitatavate dokumentide loetelu, kalap&uuml;&uuml;gilubade andmise ning kehtetuks tunnistamise korra ja kalap&uuml;&uuml;gilubade vormid kehtestab Vabariigi Valitsus. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) The list of documents to be presented upon application for a commercial fishing permit, the procedure for the issue and revocation of fishing permits and the format of fishing permits shall be established by the Government of the Republic. </inglise>
<eesti>Nimetatud kord peab sisaldama kalap&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imaluste arvutamise metoodikat. </eesti>
<inglise>The procedure shall include the method for calculating fishing possibilities. </inglise>
<eesti>(08.02.2001 j&otilde;ust.26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </eesti>
<inglise>(08.02.2001 entered into force 26.02.2001 - RT I 2001, 18, 88) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kutseliseks kalap&uuml;&uuml;giks Loode-Atlandi Kalandusorganisatsiooni (edaspidi NAFO) tsooni veealal peab taotluses n&auml;idatud kalalaeva kaptenil olema ka tunnistus NAFO reeglite tundmise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) In order to fish commercially in waters in the Regulatory Area of the Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Organisation (hereinafter NAFO), the master of the fishing vessel indicated in the application shall also have a certificate confirming his or her knowledge of the NAFO rules. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastava tunnistuse annab Keskkonnainspektsioon ja see antakse &uuml;heks aastaks. </eesti>
<inglise>The corresponding certificate shall be issued by the Environmental Inspectorate for one year. </inglise>
<eesti>NAFO reeglite tundmise tunnistuse v&auml;ljaandmise korra ja teadmiste hindamise metoodika kehtestab keskkonnaminister. </eesti>
<inglise>The procedure for the issue of certificates concerning knowledge of NAFO rules and the methods for assessing such knowledge shall be established by the Minister of the Environment. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloaga m&auml;&auml;ratakse lubatud p&uuml;&uuml;givahendid, v&auml;ljap&uuml;&uuml;gimahud, p&uuml;&uuml;giajad ja/v&otilde;i p&uuml;&uuml;gip&auml;evade arv ning kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi koht. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) The permitted fishing gear, quota allocations, fishing seasons and/or the number of fishing days, and the fishing area shall be designated in the fishing permit. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui ettev&otilde;tja on omandanud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse veealal v&auml;ljaspool Eesti Vabariigi jurisdiktsiooni, s&otilde;ltumata Eesti Vabariigist, aga kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse andja n&otilde;uab kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse kasutamiseks Eesti Vabariigi n&otilde;usolekut, m&auml;&auml;ratakse kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloaga kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi koht ja m&auml;rgitakse loale kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse omandamise alus. </eesti>
<inglise>If the undertaking has, independently of the Republic of Estonia, obtained the right to fish in waters beyond the jurisdiction of the Republic of Estonia but the granter of the right to fish requires the consent of the Republic of Estonia for the fishing right to be exercised, the fishing area shall be designated in the fishing permit and the basis for obtaining the right to fish shall be indicated in the permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) P&uuml;&uuml;gip&auml;ev k&auml;esoleva seaduse t&auml;henduses on kalendrip&auml;ev, mille sees kalalaev viibib veealal, millel kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki reguleeritakse, s&otilde;ltumata asjaolust, kas kala tegelikult p&uuml;&uuml;takse. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) For the purposes of this Act, a fishing day is a calendar day during which a fishing vessel is present in waters where fishing is regulated, regardless of whether fish are actually caught. </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi loa andmisest keeldutakse, kui: </eesti>
<inglise>(8) A commercial fishing permit shall be refused if: </inglise>
<eesti>1) loa taotlejal v&otilde;i tema nimetatud kaluril on rohkem kui &uuml;ks kehtiv halduskaristus v&otilde;i &uuml;ks kehtiv kriminaalkaristus kalap&uuml;&uuml;gin&otilde;uete rikkumise eest; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the applicant or the fisherman specified by the applicant has more than one administrative punishment in force or one criminal punishment in force for violation of fishing requirements; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa kalap&uuml;&uuml;gin&otilde;uete rikkumise t&otilde;ttu kehtetuks tunnistamisest on m&ouml;&ouml;dunud v&auml;hem kui aasta; </eesti>
<inglise>2) less than one year has passed since revocation of the fishing permit of the fishing vessel for violation of fishing requirements; </inglise>
<eesti>3) taotlus ei vasta n&otilde;uetele v&otilde;i on loa taotleja esitanud taotluses valeandmeid; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the application does not conform to the requirements or the applicant submits false information in the application; </inglise>
<eesti>4) loa taotleja on esitanud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi kohta valeandmeid v&otilde;i j&auml;tnud andmed t&auml;htaegselt esitamata; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the applicant submits false information on fishing or fails to submit the information within the set term; </inglise>
<eesti>5) loa taotleja kalalaeva ei luba kala p&uuml;&uuml;dma p&uuml;&uuml;gikohas kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki reguleerivad &otilde;igusaktid v&otilde;i p&uuml;&uuml;gikohas kalap&uuml;&uuml;ki korraldav riik v&otilde;i rahvusvaheline organisatsioon; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the fishing vessel of the applicant is not permitted to fish in the fishing area by legislation regulating fishing or by the state or international organisation regulating fishing in the fishing area; </inglise>
<eesti>6) loa taotleja on j&auml;tnud t&auml;htaegselt maksmata kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse tasu; </eesti>
<inglise>6) the applicant fails to pay the fee for the right to fish within the set term; </inglise>
<eesti>7) kalalaeva kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba taotletakse kalap&uuml;&uuml;giks v&auml;ljapoole Eesti Vabariigi jurisdiktsiooni all olevale veealale ja kalalaev ei ole varustatud laeva asukoha j&auml;lgimist v&otilde;imaldava satelliitj&auml;lgimiss&uuml;steemiga. </eesti>
<inglise>7) the fishing permit of the fishing vessel is applied for in order to fish in waters beyond the jurisdiction of the Republic of Estonia and if the fishing vessel is not equipped with a satellite monitoring system which enables the location of the vessel to be monitored. </inglise>
<eesti>(9) Kui taotleja ei ole taotletava aasta 30. aprilliks kalap&uuml;&uuml;giluba v&auml;lja v&otilde;tnud, loetakse p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imalused v&auml;lja v&otilde;tmata loa ulatuses vabanenuteks. </eesti>
<inglise>(9) If the applicant has not collected the fishing permit by 30 April of the year for which the permit is applied for, the fishing possibilities shall be considered released to the extent of the uncollected permit. </inglise>
<eesti>Vabanenud p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imalused m&uuml;&uuml;akse enampakkumisel taotletava aasta 1. juuniks. </eesti>
<inglise>Released fishing possibilities shall be sold at auction by 1 June of the year for which the permit is applied for. </inglise>
