<inglise>(5) (Repealed - 12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>(6) Kui isik on tasunud &otilde;iguse eest p&uuml;&uuml;da kala mitme erineva p&uuml;&uuml;givahendiga, v&otilde;ib ta k&otilde;iki neid p&uuml;&uuml;givahendeid samaaegselt kasutada. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) If a person has paid for the right to catch fish with several different types of fishing gear, he or she may use all those types of fishing gear at the same time. </inglise>
<eesti>(17.04.96 j&otilde;ust.24.04.96 - RT I 1996, 27, 567) </eesti>
<inglise>(17.04.96 entered into force 24.04.96 - RT I 1996, 27, 567) </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Tasu kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse, v&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;giloa ja kalastuskaardi eest kantakse riigieelarvesse. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) Fees for the right to fish, for permits to catch crayfish and for fishing cards shall be transferred to the state budget. </inglise>
<eesti>Laekunud raha kasutamise sihtotstarbe ja korra s&auml;testab seadus. </eesti>
<inglise>The specific purpose of and the procedure for the use of money received shall be provided by an Act. </inglise>
