<inglise>(16.06.99 entered into force 23.06.99 - RT I 1999, 54, 583) </inglise>
<eesti>(8) Tasu harrastusliku kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse, v&auml;hip&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse ja piiratud kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse eest tuleb maksta enne p&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igust t&otilde;endava dokumendi saamist. </eesti>
<inglise>(8) The fee for the right to fish for recreation, the right to catch crayfish, and right restricted fishing rights shall be paid prior to the receipt of a document certifying the right to fish. </inglise>
<eesti>(12.10.2000 j&otilde;ust.10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </eesti>
<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>(9) Tasu kutselise kalap&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse eest tuleb tasuda enne p&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;igust t&otilde;endava dokumendi saamist v&auml;hemalt 50-protsendiliselt. </eesti>
<inglise>(9) At least 50 per cent of the fee for the right to fish commercially shall be paid prior to the receipt of a document certifying the right to fish. </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lej&auml;&auml;nud tasu makstakse 10 p&auml;eva jooksul p&auml;rast 50 protsendi p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imaluste &auml;rakasutamist. </eesti>
<inglise>The remainder of the fee shall be paid within ten days after having used 50 per cent of the fishing possibilities. </inglise>
