<inglise>(12.10.2000 entered into force 10.11.2000 - RT I 2000, 81, 514) </inglise>
<eesti>(10) Kui kalap&uuml;&uuml;giloa andja on tunnistanud loa kehtetuks loa saanud isikust s&otilde;ltumatutel asjaoludel, tagastatakse p&uuml;&uuml;gi&otilde;iguse tasu loa saanud isikule tema poolt kasutamata j&auml;&auml;nud p&uuml;&uuml;giv&otilde;imaluste ulatuses vastavasisulise taotluse alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>(10) If the issuer of a fishing permit revokes the permit for reasons not dependent on the person who had obtained the permit, the fee for the right to fish shall be refunded to the person to the extent of the unused fishing possibilities and on the basis of a corresponding application. </inglise>
